{
  "stem": "19837.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 41.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was born in April, and he was a year old, then, when we were in Prague, the following year.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So during this year, we went from [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Nitra.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made our way to Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything before he was a year old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That year was from '38 to '39, where we were running from one country to another.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we walked to the next train station with a hand cart with a baby buggy on it and everything what he needed, and-- just like the Fiddler on the Roof in the film, That's how we left Nitra and walked to the next train station.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Went on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't care where the train went, just went on and happened to go to Prague.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got off, went to Prague, went to a hotel where a lot of other Jewish refugees were living.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we stayed there for a while, and tried to get out of Europe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who did you stay with in Prague?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the hotel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh my father-in-law, my husband, and the baby.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had one room in the hotel, and my husband ran around all day long with the rest of the people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do we know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What are we going to do now?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing is we were there legally, and so we had a little time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we tried-- one day he came home, and he said, we can go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, you have to come into the office and listen to what they have to say.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they told us if we go to Palestine, we have to go on a ship where they cover us up when other ships come around so they don't see that they had people on the ship.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
